 and none in the state scarlett paw how proud of yourself you 
 are mr well it is scarlett so been spying 
 on me and like your sister sue ellen be telling your mother on 
 me that i was jumping again 
 scarlett oh paw you know no tattle like sue ellen but it 
 does seem to me that after you broke your knee last year jumping that 
 same fence 
 mr not have me own daughter telling me what i shall 
 jump and not jump my own neck so it is 
 scarlett all right paw you jump what you please how are they all 
 over at twelve oaks 
